Author: tentaclebarn
Text: Aw...thank you that’s so sweet. I took your advice and went for a walk and it helped. I’m really honored you follow me...it’s very sweet. I just wish we could all be as kind to ourselves as we are to each other.

Author: Alexithymia115
Text: I'm so proud of you. I'm not gonna lie I follow your journey because I find everything you say fucking relatable as fuuuuuuuck. I actually recommend getting out for a walk I ate a meal that made me feel yucky and fat yesterday and walking helped get my digestive system moving which reduced the ughhhh feeling ❤❤
